{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">观察</span>&alpha;粒子、&beta;粒子的运动径迹<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">拉动活塞，云室内气体膨胀，温度降低，酒精蒸气达到过饱和状态，这时如果有粒子在室内气体中飞过，使沿途的气体分子电离，过饱和酒精蒸气就会以这些离子为核心凝结成雾滴，于是显示出射线的径迹。</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">威尔逊云室</span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.打开威尔逊云室开关；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.向左拉动左侧拉杆，观察云室内</span>&alpha;粒子的运动径迹<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.在属性中切换类型为</span>&beta;粒子，向左拉动左侧拉杆，观察云室内&beta;粒子的运动径迹。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&alpha;粒子的运动径迹直而粗，&beta;粒子的运动径迹是弯曲的，比较细</span></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">&alpha;粒子质量较大，在气体中飞行时不易改变方向，且它的电离本领大，沿途产生的离子多，所以运动径迹直而粗；&beta;粒子质量小，跟气体碰撞时容易改变方向，且电离本领小，沿途产生的离子少，所以径迹是弯曲的，比较细。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}